body_html:
Looks like a leftover old protobuf installation lingering on the system.
It would be nice to understand it fully, but in reality with the volume of issues, we wont have time to dig deeper into this.
Also, for future reference, anyone seeing this problem should just purge their TF and protobuf installations and reinstall.
